OL,3,CWater bills to rise by an average of
OL,4,C#31 a year over next five years
OL,6,FHousehold water bills will increase by
OL,7,Fan average of #31 a year by 2030, with
OL,8,FSouthern Water bills to rise by more
OL,9,Fthan 50% in that time, as ITV News'
OL,10,FEllie Pitt reports
OL,12,FHousehold water bills in England and
OL,13,FWales will increase by an average of
OL,14,F#31 a year over the next five years,
OL,15,Fregulator Ofwat has announced.
OL,17,FThe proposed bill rise is
OL,18,Fsignificantly higher than the expected
OL,19,Faverage increase of around #20 a year
OL,20,Fper household, outlined in the
OL,21,Fregulator's draft proposals in July.
