OL,3,CWater bills to rise by an average of
OL,4,C#31 a year over next five years
OL,6,FOfwat said the increase would pay for
OL,7,Fa #104 billion upgrade of the water
OL,8,Fsector to deliver "substantial,
OL,9,Flasting, improvements for customers
OL,10,Fand the environment".
OL,12,FDespite the average #31 a year
OL,13,Fincrease figure, households will face
OL,14,Fa heavy average hike of #86 or 20% in
OL,15,Fthe next year, excluding inflation,
OL,16,Ffollowed by smaller increases over the
OL,17,Fnext four years.
OL,19,FThe average bill will rise by a total
OL,20,Fof #157 or 36% in the next five years.
