OL,3,CWater bills to rise by an average of
OL,4,C#31 a year over next five years
OL,6,F"This Labour Government will ringfence
OL,7,Fmoney earmarked for investment so it
OL,8,Fcan never be diverted for bonuses and
OL,9,Fshareholder payouts. We will clean up
OL,10,Four rivers, lakes and seas for good."
OL,12,FOfwat chief executive David Black
OL,13,Fsaid: "Today marks a significant
OL,14,Fmoment. It provides water companies
OL,15,Fwith an opportunity to regain
OL,16,Fcustomers' trust by using this #104
OL,17,Fbillion upgrade to turn around their
OL,18,Fenvironmental record and improve
OL,19,Fservices to customers.
