OL,3,CWater bills to rise by an average of
OL,4,C#31 a year over next five years
OL,6,F"Water companies now need to rise to
OL,7,Fthis challenge, customers will rightly
OL,8,Fexpect them to show they can deliver
OL,9,Fsignificant improvement over time to
OL,10,Fjustify the increase in bills.
OL,12,F"We recognise it is a difficult time
OL,13,Ffor many, and we are acutely aware of
OL,14,Fthe impact that bill increases will
OL,15,Fhave for some customers. That is why
OL,16,Fit is vital that companies are
OL,17,Fstepping up their support for
OL,18,Fcustomers who struggle to pay."
