OL,11,FMike Keil, chief executive of the
OL,12,FConsumer Council for Water (CCW),
OL,13,Fcalled for a social tariff and better
OL,14,Fsupport for Brits who will bear the
OL,15,Ffinancial brunt of the increase in
OL,16,Fbills.
OL,18,F"These bill rises may be less than
OL,19,Fwhat water companies wanted but they
OL,20,Fare still more than what many people
OL,21,Fcan afford," explained.
